						<summary>

						<p>c. 13th to 15th Century.</p>						

						<p>Mentions the persons who gifted the pillars. Among them are found merchants and <hi rend="italic">araiyar</hi> from different places like Perumpuliyūr, Tuvaraṅkōṭṭai, etc.</p>						

